                This code compiles but produces a VerifyError when run. The problem seems to be with the way we have combined the primary pattern within () of a condition. This
                results in us creating a GuardedPattern as following:

                GuardedPattern -)
                Primary -) String a a.equals("a")
                Condition -) a != null

                I am not sure if this is right. I think regardless of the parenthesis, we should consider as below:

                GuardedPattern -)
                Primary -) String a
                Condition -) a.equals("a") a != null

